Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.32,0:00:54.41,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}wow wow wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.64,0:00:56.92,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Break up foreordination!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.92,0:01:01.73,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Fake… あの火は仲間か?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.99,0:01:06.48,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}進むべきは闇か?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.08,0:01:11.97,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Knife 突き立てた先に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.12,0:01:15.85,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}正体の見えぬ感情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.04,0:01:21.66,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}-今はまだここで終われない-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.66,0:01:26.80,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}ならば生きる準備をしろよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.92,0:01:32.05,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}堆(うずたか)く積み上げてく熱情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.05,0:01:36.62,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}重たいに決まってんだろう?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.52,0:01:37.87,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5\pos(640,660)}{\fad(200,200)}wake up your tough intention!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.00,0:01:42.25,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}未熟だと笑うが良いさ 戦場
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.25,0:01:48.88,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}一つずつ確かめてやるから
